Nat Pendleton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nat_Pendleton 0 Nathaniel Greene "Nat" Pendleton (August 9, 1895 – October 12, 1967) was an American Olympic wrestler and film actor. His younger brother was Edmund J. Pendleton (1899-1987), the organist and composer.
